settings.editor: Brighten someone’s day with a gorgeous hand-tied spring flower bouquet from Anaïs

settings.testimonial_content:
“Anaïs Flowers are distinct, effeminate, chic, and just all around classic. Their designers have serious talent and are always such a pleasure to work with. 
A refreshing presence indeed.”

settings.editor: Forty years ago, our family opened a small flower shop in Union Square. As our family grew, so did our business. Today we have two full service flower shops in Chelsea and Midtown, steps from Grand Central Terminal. We have two dedicated teams, each specializing in Weddings and Corporate Services. Our designs have won numerous awards including Teleflora’s Top 5o Florists in the U.S. We have built long lasting relationships with local growers and searched for the best quality flowers to bring back to our clients. Our commitment has stood the test of time and we continue to build our family business.
Flowers always make people better, happier, they are sunshine and medicine for the soul.
